{{EngvarB|date=November 2015}} {{Use dmy dates|date=November 2015}} {{Infobox government agency | seal = Ministry of Agriculture and Irrigation.svg | seal_caption = Seal of the Ministry of Agriculture and Irrigation | logo = | formed = <!-- {{Start date|df=yes|YYYY|MM|DD}} --> | preceding1 = [[Ministry of Agriculture, Livestock and Irrigation (Myanmar)]] | preceding2 = | dissolved = | jurisdiction = [[Government of Myanmar]] | headquarters = [[Naypyidaw]] | coordinates = {{coord|19.7862975|96.1141331|type:landmark|display=inline}} | employees = | budget = | minister1_name = Dr.[[Aung Thu (minister)|Aung Thu ]] | deputyminister1_name = Dr. Tun Win | deputyminister2_name = <!-- (etc.) --> | chief1_name = | chief1_position = | chief2_name = | chief2_position = <!-- (etc.) --> | chief3_name = | chief3_position = | chief4_name = | chief4_position = | chief5_name = | chief5_position = | chief6_name = | chief6_position = | chief7_name = | chief7_position = | chief8_name = | chief8_position = | chief9_name = | chief9_position = | parent_department = | parent_agency = | child1_agency = Minister's Office | child2_agency = Water Resource Utilisation Department | child3_agency = Department of Agriculture | child4_agency = Irrigation Department | child5_agency = Agricultural Mechanisation Department | child6_agency = Settlement and Land Record Department | child7_agency = Department of Agricultural Planning | child8_agency = Myanma Agricultural Development Bank | child9_agency = Department of Agriculture Research | child10_agency = Yezin Agricultural University | child11_agency = Department of Industrial Crops Development | child12_agency = Department of Cooperative<!-- (etc.) --> | keydocument1 = <!-- (etc.) --> | website = {{URL|www.moai.gov.mm}} | map = | map_caption = | footnotes = | agency_type = | agency_name = Ministry of Agriculture and Irrigation | nativename = {{my|လယ်ယာစိုက်ပျိုးရေးနှင့် ဆည်မြောင်း ဝန်ကြီးဌာန}} | nativename_r = | seal_width = | picture = | picture_width = | picture_caption = | superseding = Ministry of Agriculture | map_width = }}
The '''Ministry of Agriculture and Irrigation''' (MOLI) is a [[Ministry (government department)|ministry]] in the [[Burmese government]] responsible for [[agriculture]] and [[irrigation]]. Until 8 August 1996, it was named the Ministry of Agriculture.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.modins.net/myanmarinfo/ministry/agriculture.htm|title=Ministry Of Agriculture and Irrigation|year=2002|publisher=Myanmar Online Data Information Network Solutions|accessdate=18 April 2012}}</ref>In 2016, President Htin Kyaw composed it with the [[Ministry of Livestock, Fisheries and Rural Development]] as [[Ministry of Agriculture, Livestock and Irrigation (Myanmar)|Ministry of Agriculture, Livestock and Irrigation]].
== Departments == * Minister's Office * Department of Agriculture * Irrigation and Water Utilization Management Department * Agricultural Mechanisation Department * Department of Agriculture Land Management and Statistics * Department of Planning * Myanma Agricultural Development Bank * Department of Agriculture Research * [[Yezin Agricultural University]] * Department of Industrial Crops Development * Department of Cooperative * Department of Fisheries
